        <h1>What To Expect</h1>

        <div class="img-text-component">
          <img class="img" src="/assets/images/women-rejoicing.png" alt="Mixology class" />
          <div class="text">
            <p>
              Our two-hour classes are designed to immerse you in the world of mixology.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>
                <strong class="bold">Craft Three Signature Cocktails</strong>: Under our expert guidance, you'll learn
                how to mix, shake, and stir like a pro.
              </li>
              <li>
