                cocktail and its ingredients.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="bold">All-Inclusive Experience</strong>: We provide everything you need—recipe cards, a
                personal cocktail making kit, and top-quality ingredients.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong class="bold">Musical Vibes</strong>: Enjoy a curated playlist that keeps the energy high and the
                creativity flowing.
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Whether you're here for a solo date night, fun outing with friends, a special date, or a corporate
              event, our classes cater to all.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="booking-cta">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to book your next class?</h2>

        <div class="cta-wrapper">
          <p>Want to host a private class?</p>
          <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary request-our-services-cta">Request a class</a>

          <p>Register for an upcoming cocktail class in Orlando, FL</p>
          <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/o/sunny-mixers-82180936683"
